{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium Shopify section called "Complete Recovery System" that automatically pulls products selected from the Shopify Theme Editor.
    
    IMPORTANT:
    This section must NOT use hardcoded products.
    Allow the merchant to select exactly 3 products from the Shopify store using Product Picker blocks in the Theme Editor.
    
    Section settings:
    - Bundle title
    - Bundle description
    - Bundle CTA text
    - Bundle CTA link
    - Optional bundle savings text (e.g. "SAVE $27")
    - Optional free shipping text
    
    Product blocks:
    - Product 1 (Step 01)
    - Product 2 (Step 02)
    - Product 3 (Step 03)
    
    Each block should use a Shopify product selector so merchants can choose any product from the store.
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    DESIGN STYLE
    
    Luxury skincare / premium wellness aesthetic.
    
    - Warm ivory background
    - Soft editorial photography style
    - Large horizontal layout
    - Elegant serif heading
    - Refined muted color palette
    - Premium DTC brand feel
    - Minimalist luxury design
    - Soft shadows
    - Sophisticated spacing
    - High-end Shopify storefront aesthetic
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    LAYOUT
    
    Desktop:
    Two-column layout.
    
    LEFT SIDE (Bundle Information)
    
    Small eyebrow text:
    "NOT SURE WHERE TO START?"
    
    Large elegant serif headline:
    "Complete Recovery System"
    
    Short supporting description.
    
    Price area:
    - Bundle price
    - Compare-at price
    - Optional savings badge
    
    Primary CTA button:
    "EXPLORE THE BUNDLE"
    
    Below CTA:
    Free shipping note.
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    RIGHT SIDE (3-Step Product System)
    
    Display the three selected Shopify products as a visual progression.
    
    Layout:
    
    Product 1 → Product 2 → Product 3
    
    Between each product:
    - Minimal arrow icon
    - Spacious alignment
    - Clear visual flow
    
    Each product card should automatically pull:
    
    - Product image
    - Product title
    - Product metafield or custom step label
    - Product metafield or custom short description
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    PRODUCT STRUCTURE
    
    STEP 01
    
    Display:
    01
    
    Custom label example:
    SOOTHE
    
    Pull from selected Shopify product:
    - Featured image
    - Product title
    
    Optional metafields:
    - Day range
    - Benefit text
    
    Example:
    
    01 SOOTHE
    Hydro Gel
    Day 1–3
    Cool, calm and protect the skin.
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    STEP 02
    
    Display:
    02
    
    Custom label example:
    REGENERATE
    
    Pull from selected Shopify product.
    
    Example:
    
    02 REGENERATE
    Recovery Mist
    Day 4–10
    Repair, regenerate and relieve itch.
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    STEP 03
    
    Display:
    03
    
    Custom label example:
    MAINTAIN
    
    Pull from selected Shopify product.
    
    Example:
    
    03 MAINTAIN
    Daily Care Balm
    Day 11+
    Strengthen barrier and lock in moisture.
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    BOTTOM BENEFITS BAR
    
    Full-width benefits strip beneath the section.
    
    4 columns.
    
    Each benefit includes:
    - Minimal line icon
    - Small uppercase title
    - Supporting description
    
    Examples:
    
    CIRCADIAN ALIGNED
    Works with your skin's natural rhythm.
    
    BIOLOGICAL SEQUENCE
    Each stage supports the next.
    
    CLINICALLY TESTED
    Safe and effective for new tattoos.
    
    CONSCIOUS BY DESIGN
    Minimal impact. Maximum care.
    
    Allow all benefit content to be editable from Theme Editor.
    
    --------------------------------------------------
    
    SHOPIFY REQUIREMENTS
    
    - Shopify Online Store 2.0 compatible
    - Merchant selects products directly from Shopify Product Picker
    - Pull product images dynamically
    - Pull product titles dynamically
    - Optional metafield support for:
      - Step Name
      - Day Range
      - Benefit Description
    - Fully responsive
    - Mobile: stack products vertically
    - Desktop: horizontal progression layout
    - Maintain premium luxury aesthetic
    - Optimized for Dawn theme and Shopify AI generation, make the bundle to be selectable as a product as well
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-recovery-system-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 0 0;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1340px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-eyebrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_font }}, sans-serif;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_size }}px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.heading_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.heading_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.heading_font.weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-price-area-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.price_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-compare-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.price_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.compare_price_color }};
    text-decoration: line-through;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-savings-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.savings_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.savings_text_color }};
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

 .ai-recovery-system-{{ ai_gen_id }} .btn.btn--primary {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_bg_color }} !important;
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-shipping-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: {{ block.settings.shipping_text_color }};
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-right-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-product-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    max-width: 200px;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-step-number-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-style:italic;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: {{ block.settings.step_number_color }};
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-step-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: {{ block.settings.step_label_color }};
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 8px;
    height:100%;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-product-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-product-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 60%;
    height: 60%;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-product-meta-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: {{ block.settings.meta_text_color }};
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: {{ block.settings.arrow_color }};
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-benefits-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.benefits_bg_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.benefits_padding }}px 20px;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-benefits-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1340px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-benefit-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-benefit-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: {{ block.settings.benefit_icon_color }};
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-benefit-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-benefit-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: {{ block.settings.benefit_title_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-recovery-system-benefit-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: {{ block.settings.benefit_text_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-recovery-system-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .ai-recovery-system-right-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .ai-recovery-system-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }

    .ai-recovery-system-product-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      max-width: 100%;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .ai-recovery-system-benefits-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .ai-recovery-system-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-recovery-system-benefits-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }
  }
  .ai-recovery-system-{{ ai_gen_id }} .underline{
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
{% endstyle %}

<ai-recovery-system-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-recovery-system-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-recovery-system-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-recovery-system-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-recovery-system-left-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.eyebrow_text != blank %}
          <p class="ai-recovery-system-eyebrow-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.eyebrow_text }}</p>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
          <h2 class="ai-recovery-system-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.description != blank %}
          <div class="ai-recovery-system-description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.description }}</div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.bundle_product != blank %}
          <div class="ai-recovery-system-price-area-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <span class="ai-recovery-system-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.bundle_product.price | money }}</span>
            {% if block.settings.bundle_product.compare_at_price > block.settings.bundle_product.price %}
              <span class="ai-recovery-system-compare-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.bundle_product.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.savings_text != blank %}
              <span class="ai-recovery-system-savings-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.savings_text }}</span>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% elsif block.settings.bundle_price != blank or block.settings.compare_price != blank %}
          <div class="ai-recovery-system-price-area-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if block.settings.bundle_price != blank %}
              <span class="ai-recovery-system-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.bundle_price }}</span>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.compare_price != blank %}
              <span class="ai-recovery-system-compare-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.compare_price }}</span>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.savings_text != blank %}
              <span class="ai-recovery-system-savings-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.savings_text }}</span>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.cta_text != blank %}
          <div>
            {% if block.settings.bundle_product != blank %}
              <a href="{{ block.settings.bundle_product.url }}" class=" btn btn--primary">
                {{ block.settings.cta_text }}
              </a>
            {% elsif block.settings.cta_link != blank %}
              <a href="{{ block.settings.cta_link }}" class="btn btn--primary">
                {{ block.settings.cta_text }}
              </a>
            {% else %}
              <a href="#" class="btn btn--primary">
                {{ block.settings.cta_text }}
              </a>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.shipping_text != blank %}
              <p class="ai-recovery-system-shipping-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.shipping_text }}</p>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="ai-recovery-system-right-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.product_1 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div>
              <div class="ai-recovery-system-step-number-{{ ai_gen_id }}">01</div>
              {% if block.settings.step_1_label != blank %}
                <div class="ai-recovery-system-step-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step_1_label }}</div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            {% if block.settings.product_1.featured_image %}
              <img
                src="{{ block.settings.product_1.featured_image | image_url: width: 400 }}"
                alt="{{ block.settings.product_1.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                class="ai-recovery-system-product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="400"
                height="400"
              >
            {% else %}
              <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
              </div>
            {% endif %}
            <h3 class="ai-recovery-system-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.product_1.title }}</h3>
            {% if block.settings.step_1_meta != blank %}
              <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-meta-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step_1_meta }}</div>
            {% endif %}
             <a href="{{ block.settings.product_1.url }}" class="underline">Learn more</a>
          </div>
        {% else %}
          <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div>
              <div class="ai-recovery-system-step-number-{{ ai_gen_id }}">01</div>
              {% if block.settings.step_1_label != blank %}
                <div class="ai-recovery-system-step-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step_1_label }}</div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
            </div>
            <h3 class="ai-recovery-system-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Select Product 1</h3>
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ai-recovery-system-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
            <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>

        {% if block.settings.product_2 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div>
              <div class="ai-recovery-system-step-number-{{ ai_gen_id }}">02</div>
              {% if block.settings.step_2_label != blank %}
                <div class="ai-recovery-system-step-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step_2_label }}</div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            {% if block.settings.product_2.featured_image %}
              <img
                src="{{ block.settings.product_2.featured_image | image_url: width: 400 }}"
                alt="{{ block.settings.product_2.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                class="ai-recovery-system-product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="400"
                height="400"
              >
            {% else %}
              <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
              </div>
            {% endif %}
            <h3 class="ai-recovery-system-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.product_2.title }}</h3>
            {% if block.settings.step_2_meta != blank %}
              <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-meta-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step_2_meta }}</div>
            {% endif %}
             <a href="{{ block.settings.product_2.url }}" class="underline">Learn more</a>

          </div>
        {% else %}
          <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div>
              <div class="ai-recovery-system-step-number-{{ ai_gen_id }}">02</div>
              {% if block.settings.step_2_label != blank %}
                <div class="ai-recovery-system-step-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step_2_label }}</div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
            </div>
            <h3 class="ai-recovery-system-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Select Product 2</h3>
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ai-recovery-system-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
            <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>

        {% if block.settings.product_3 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div>
              <div class="ai-recovery-system-step-number-{{ ai_gen_id }}">03</div>
              {% if block.settings.step_3_label != blank %}
                <div class="ai-recovery-system-step-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step_3_label }}</div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            {% if block.settings.product_3.featured_image %}
              <img
                src="{{ block.settings.product_3.featured_image | image_url: width: 400 }}"
                alt="{{ block.settings.product_3.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                class="ai-recovery-system-product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="400"
                height="400"
              >
            {% else %}
              <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
              </div>
            {% endif %}
            <h3 class="ai-recovery-system-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.product_3.title }}</h3>
            {% if block.settings.step_3_meta != blank %}
              <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-meta-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step_3_meta }}</div>
            {% endif %}
             <a href="{{ block.settings.product_3.url }}" class="underline">Learn more</a>

          </div>
        {% else %}
          <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div>
              <div class="ai-recovery-system-step-number-{{ ai_gen_id }}">03</div>
              {% if block.settings.step_3_label != blank %}
                <div class="ai-recovery-system-step-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step_3_label }}</div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="ai-recovery-system-product-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
            </div>
            <h3 class="ai-recovery-system-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Select Product 3</h3>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ai-recovery-system-benefits-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-recovery-system-benefits-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.benefit_1_title != blank %}
        <div class="ai-recovery-system-benefit-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-recovery-system-benefit-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="ai-recovery-system-benefit-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.benefit_1_title }}</h4>
          {% if block.settings.benefit_1_description != blank %}
            <p class="ai-recovery-system-benefit-description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.benefit_1_description }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.benefit_2_title != blank %}
        <div class="ai-recovery-system-benefit-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-recovery-system-benefit-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="ai-recovery-system-benefit-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.benefit_2_title }}</h4>
          {% if block.settings.benefit_2_description != blank %}
            <p class="ai-recovery-system-benefit-description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.benefit_2_description }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.benefit_3_title != blank %}
        <div class="ai-recovery-system-benefit-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-recovery-system-benefit-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
